# Privacy Policy - Housy Inspect

**Effective Date:** January 9, 2026
**Last Updated:** January 9, 2026

## About This App

Housy Inspect is an internal enterprise application exclusively for Pro Housypoint Tech Solutions Pvt Ltd employees. This app is not available to the public and requires company-issued credentials.

## Information We Collect

- Employee login credentials and work-related data
- Location data during work hours for attendance tracking
- Property inspection photos, videos, and voice notes
- Device information for app functionality

## How We Use Your Information

- Employee attendance and task management
- Property inspection documentation and reporting
- App performance and technical support
- Company operational requirements

## Data Security

- All data is encrypted and stored on secure company servers
- Access restricted to authorized company personnel only
- Data automatically syncs with company systems
- Your account is deactivated when employment ends

## Data Sharing

We do not share your personal information with third parties. Data is used internally for:
- Work assignment and performance management
- Client inspection reports (property data only, not personal employee data)
- Legal compliance when required by law

## Employee Rights

- Access to your personal data upon request
- Right to correct inaccurate information
- Data retention as per company policy and legal requirements
- Contact HR or IT support for data-related requests

## Contact

For privacy questions or support:
- **Email:** support@housypoint.com
- **Internal IT:** Available to company employees
- **HR Department:** hr@housypoint.com

## Important Notice

This application is for authorized Pro Housypoint Tech Solutions employees only. Unauthorized access is prohibited.

